(replPure x st)=(st, x)

= (replTraverse act inputs st)
^ rowTraverseState st _ inputs v2
& (st inp yield)
: newSt vl < replCase (act inp st)
| yield newSt vl

=?= (%[], [3 4 5]) (replTraverse replPure [3 4 5] %[])

= (readAppExpr readExpr env rex st)
: st params
    < ^ replOpen _ st
      | replTraverse (readExpr env) (rexKids rex)
^ (st, _)
# switch len-params
* 0 | K 0
